      <title>弗雷迪·麦克（Freddie Mac）告诉工人全职返回办公室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/fhfa-director-calls-freddie-mac-workers-back-to-office-full-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗雷迪·麦克（Freddie Mac）告诉员工，他们将每周从5月开始五天从办公室工作，并承诺审查薪酬计划，以奖励关键人物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/fhfa-director-calls-freddie-mac-workers-back-to-office-full-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 00:42:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多年的煤炭反弹破坏了印度的能源安全推动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/years-of-coal-backlash-undermine-india-s-energy-security-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了满足其不断增长的能源需求，印度扩大世界上最大的煤炭动力舰队之一的计划是由于能够和愿意帮助建造新工厂的公司而撤销的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/years-of-coal-backlash-undermine-india-s-energy-security-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 00:21:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
